Package com.umidity.api.caller

Interface ApiListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
MainGui
public interface ApiListener
Api event listener interface.
Implement this interface whenever you need to handle ApiCaller events. This may find real usage when using an AsyncCaller.
To add your listener to the "list of listeners" of an ApiCaller instance, just call the addListener(yourListener) method.
